                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150913-202-off1122 t18150913-202-crimeloc1124"></join>. Part of my house was consumed in the great fire. I saw the articles named in the indictment safe before the fire. I did not see the prisoners there. The next time. I saw the articles were at the Mansion House.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18150913-202-person1796">
                  ELLEN 
                  LYON
               <interp inst="t18150913-202-person1796" type="surname" value="LYON"></interp>
