            . I also inhabited a house consumed by the fire. I lost a great many things, some of which were burnt, and a great many stolen.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18150913-202-person1797">
                  WILLIAM 
                  NORTON
               <interp inst="t18150913-202-person1797" type="surname" value="NORTON"></interp>
